<section class="faq-section">
    <div class="faq-inner">

        <div class="faq-image">
            <img src="/images/training2.jpg" alt="Gym training" />
        </div>

        <div class="faq-content">
            <span class="faq-badge">+ Frequently Asked Questions</span>
            <h2 class="faq-title">Common questions about<br>gym and training</h2>

            <div class="faq-list">

                <div class="faq-item active">
                    <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
                        <span>Q1. Do I need prior gym experience to Join CoreFitness?</span>
                        <span class="faq-icon">&#x2303;</span>
                    </button>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>No, GymPro is designed for all fitness levels. Our trainers guide beginners with proper techniques and structured workout plans to help them start safely and confidently.</p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Every new member receives a personalized introduction to equipments</li>
                            <li>Workouts are designed to grow with you, ensuring beginners can start safely.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
                        <span>Q2. What facilities are included with the membership?</span>
                        <span class="faq-icon">&#x2304;</span>
                    </button>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>All memberships include access to our full gym floor, locker rooms, showers, and group fitness classes. Premium members also get access to the sauna and dedicated training zones.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
                        <span>Q3. Can I try the gym before taking a membership?</span>
                        <span class="faq-icon">&#x2304;</span>
                    </button>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Yes! We offer a free 1-week trial for all new visitors. No credit card required — just sign up and come in to experience everything CoreFitness has to offer.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
                        <span>Q4. Are there group workout programs available?</span>
                        <span class="faq-icon">&#x2304;</span>
                    </button>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Absolutely. We run daily group classes including HIIT, yoga, spin, and strength circuits. Classes are included in all membership tiers.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="faq-item">
                    <button class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
                        <span>Q5. Is nutrition guidance included in the plans?</span>
                        <span class="faq-icon">&#x2304;</span>
                    </button>
                    <div class="faq-answer">
                        <p>Premium members receive a personalized nutrition consultation with one of our certified coaches. Standard members can access our nutrition guide library online.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>

    </div>
</section>

<script>
    function toggleFaq(btn) {
        const item = btn.closest('.faq-item');
        const isActive = item.classList.contains('active');

        document.querySelectorAll('.faq-item').forEach(i => {
            i.classList.remove('active');
            i.querySelector('.faq-icon').innerHTML = '&#x2304;';
        });

        if (!isActive) {
            item.classList.add('active');
            btn.querySelector('.faq-icon').innerHTML = '&#x2303;';
        }
    }
</script>
